SubjectOnion Lake Indian Reserve No. 119-2 Seekaskootch Indian Reserve No. 119 Makaoo Indian Reserve No. 120, in the Province of Saskatchewan ** DESIGNATION **
PrecisOrder accepting a DESIGNATION for commercial and/or industrial purposes of approximately 124.40 hectares (307.43 acres) of land on ONION LAKE INDIAN RESERVE No. 119-2, SEEKASKOOTCH INDIAN RESERVE No. 119 and MAKAOO INDIAN RESERVE No. 120, in Saskatchewan.
